attributes.review: I had high expectations of this app and was deeply disappointed. The app opened with Donald Trump telling me to vote for him or he’s gonna rape his wife. I don’t want to be responsible for his wife’s rape but I can’t support someone who rapes women and think it’s ok to rape. I hope he gets arrested for the rest of his life to serve for his crimes. The app also gave me nightmares with the disturbing images of people cutting their wrist in an attempt to kill themselves. I need this app to get banned because he is promoting self harm and that could be very triggering for anyone.
